## 4. Graph schema

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  T[Technique] -->|REQUIRES optional?| P[Permission]
  T -->|INVOKES| M[ApiMethod]
  P -->|MAPS_TO| M
  R[DetectionRule] -->|COVERS| M
  T -->|DETECTED_BY| R
  T -->|GRANTS| C[Capability]
  C -->|IMPLIES| C
  C -->|UNLOCKS| T
  T -->|ENABLES| T
  T -->|IN_TACTIC| TA[Tactic]
  T -->|FOR_SERVICE| S[Service]
```

- **`ApiMethod`** carries `log_type` (`ADMIN_ACTIVITY` / `DATA_ACCESS`), `logged_by_default`
  and `has_technique` (is any technique invoking it).
- **`DETECTED_BY`** and **`ENABLES`** are *derived* at build time; everything else is extracted
  from the corpora.
- **Workspace rules** key on admin/login `eventName`s (a different telemetry stream) and by
  construction cover **0** GCP-API operations — they exist as nodes but contribute no coverage.

